{"tid":1130700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿兒子遭廢老抓傷 任職地產經紀男子一拳打死7旬翁","createTime":"2019-04-29T08:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T09:10:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d2cda0679575ae3c397cb578ec2bc9521e3689ab","tid":1130700,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"2019.04.29 15:39<br />\n(澳門電台消息) 36歲地產經紀懷疑因不滿兒子在休憩區被另 1男童抓傷，揮拳打傷男童的 74歲外公，男童外公最終傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n司警表示，嫌疑人陪同 5歲兒子到下環街市內的休憩區玩耍，兒子期間被 1名9歲男童抓傷，因嫌疑人要與男童父母理論，男童將嫌疑人帶返自己位於打鐵斜巷的住所，同住的外公拒絕賠償並表示要報警。有人揮動右拳擊中男童外公左面面頰，男童外公送院後證實腦出血及腦水腫，延至昨日 (28日) 早上不治。<br />\n<br />\n司警稱，嫌疑人承認一時氣憤犯罪，由於動機微不足道，涉嫌觸犯嚴重傷害他人身體完整性及因結果之加重，將他移交檢察院。若罪名成立，最高可被判監 20年。 (鄺惠敏  黃偉鴻)"},{"pid":"65e6f4ca44d59c89d32a44b7ccc97f3b17a784fe","tid":1130700,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"好男人"},{"pid":"261b798225513e611b1525afea694c78b600c6c3","tid":1130700,"uid":65686,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"真&middot;一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf34cd880c98cc5936d08edfc3f0d92e367427a","tid":1130700,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"勇武澳門男 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5842b30d4dcf92239752258c6845fe846d0fbd52","tid":1130700,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/18la1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2F18la1p1.jpg&h=f27897ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名5歲男童與另一名9歲男童上周六下午在下環街市休憩區玩樂時發生碰撞，5歲男童踩對方一腳，9歲男童還手抓傷對方。5歲男童在場的36歲父親得悉事件後大怒，要求聯絡9歲男童家長不果後，登門到達對方位於事發現場附近的住處興師問罪。開門的是與9歲男童一同居住的74歲外公，涉案躁父要求對方賠償，外公拒絕及表示希望報警處理事件時，涉案躁父即時大怒，當著9歲男童面前一拳重擊其外公頭部，外公隨即倒地暈倒及腦部出血。最後經鄰居發現報案送院搶救，可惜延至周日早上因傷重不治返魂乏術。"},{"pid":"fc463cbd940504152ab954b82456f7778830f3c1","tid":1130700,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"幅圖似地產狗互路多d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0918ca18f6451d6dee7c88f9f90d76f0ed676dd","tid":1130700,"uid":108199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:37:13.000Z","msg":"諗到廢老的嘴臉<br />\n好多乜都唔知就幫住自己的仆街細路<br />\n仲屈返人轉頭"},{"pid":"66483165e757b754732c7ccb557a32b39c40add2","tid":1130700,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"261b798225513e611b1525afea694c78b600c6c3","tid":1130700,"uid":65686,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"真&middot;一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/17fca2c25f96f224b67cc7729b3bfed3d9330f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.hdslb.com%2Fbfs%2Farchive%2F17fca2c25f96f224b67cc7729b3bfed3d9330f68.jpg&h=16f9adeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86aa5d741c854e373879d55903e1184eb6da4bb1","tid":1130700,"uid":9013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"又地產"},{"pid":"2352231e508a9b6e68062e498097cdf08ca51538","tid":1130700,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黎香港做啦"},{"pid":"a78cc2fa93893ccf1cded98a041f56aa05cdf2d9","tid":1130700,"uid":52459,"like":0,"